name: CAES Simulator
body:
### Welcome to CAES Simulation

Project Lead: Kevin E. Anderson (@k3a-uw)
Research Assistants: 
Committee: Dr. George Mobus (University of Washington-Tacoma), Dr. Wayne Wakeland (Portland State University)

### Overview
The CAES Simulator serves to allow the creation and simulation of complex models using a simple yet unique modeling language that combines methods of Stock and Flow models with Agent Based modeling.
